==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dewclaw
<hw>Dew"claw`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>In any animal, esp.
of the Herbivora, a rudimentary claw or small hoof not reaching the
ground.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Some cut off the <qex>dewclaws</qex> [of greyhounds].</q>
<rj><qau>J. H. Walsh.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dewdrop</ent>⟦br⟧
